  }, "Fortumo"), " where he focuses on designing and building payment integration applications deployed on AWS."), mdx("h3", {
    "id": "tell-us-about-yourself"
  }, mdx("strong", {
    parentName: "h3"
  }, "Tell us about yourself")), mdx("h4", {
    "id": "how-long-have-you-been-coding-what-got-you-interested-what-languagesdbs-have-been-your-focus"
